Kotlin 2.1.21 is out now!

This release includes bug fixes following the recent 2.1.20 tooling update.

Since Kotlin 2.0.0, releases are structured as:

2.x.0 – Language releases (major updates, every 6 months)

2.x.20 – Tooling releases (updates & fixes, mid-cycle)

2.x.yz – Bug fix releases (as needed)

